dc_description_s:
194 MB ZIP FILE, contains a single seamless MrSID image.  Digital orthophotos combine the geometric qualities of a map with the image 
qualities of a photograph. The imagery collected during this flight has a ground 
resolution of 2 US foot x 2 US Foot at a scale of 1:1700. The 
image is a mosaic of the entire county and has a geographic extent of 202,239 x 
161,121 feet, with a 300-foot buffer around the County and is available in MrSID 
format. Individual township MrSID images are also available.
